### Health
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Login (Admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Set token variable in your client after login
# @token = paste_token_here

### List users
GET http://localhost:3000/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create user
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Faculty",
  "email": "newfac@example.com",
  "role": "faculty",
  "password": "password",
  "department": "CSE"
}

### List courses
GET http://localhost:3000/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Generate timetable (2 choices)
POST http://localhost:3000/timetable/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "choices": 2 }

### Get choices
GET http://localhost:3000/timetable/choices
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Conflicts and suggestions (on latest)
POST http://localhost:3000/timetable/conflicts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Approve a choice
POST http://localhost:3000/timetable/review
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "approvedId": "tt-id-from-choices" }



